wikimedia-globalblocking-ipblocked:
'''Nunga [[m:Special:MyLanguage/Global blocks|diambati di sude wiki]] do alamat IP-mi.'''

Dibahen $1 ($2) do pangambatonna.
Marhitehite "$3".

*Mulamula diambati: $4
*Ujung ni pangambaton: $5

Alamat IP-mi saonari i ma $6.
Dohothon sude harharon di ganup panungkunanmi.

Molo adong hasalaan di nasa pangambatonmi, boi dipadomu hamu do inpormasi na lobian jala patuduhon di [[m:Special:MyLanguage/No open proxies|ndada proksi tarbuka]] habisukon global.
Molo soada, hatahon hamu salpu [[m:Steward requests/Global|manongos pangidoan asa boi dipareso di Meta-Wiki]].
